{
  "stem": "1641.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 1.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had-- once a day, we had a small-- say, half a liter of baked bean soup-- you know, bean soup, but not too much beans in it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the beans were rotten.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were all very old stock.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were all past the use-by date.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they were-- everybody got diarrhea from it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was the only food we-- we had every day, the baked bean soup.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, we didn't have much to do all day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were just standing around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I became friendly with one of the Jewish girls.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She was 18, just finished her [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "HSC. ?] And we spent a day together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in the evening, she invited me to her family's place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there, I could see, in one room, about 60 or 80 people, her whole family-- including grandmothers, grandparents, uncles, great-aunts, and cousins and everybody.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they will be sitting around the table.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I took part in their-- what-- they had some food left, some little bread, and other things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- and then the old people were discussing-- they were very sad.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Most of them were crying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And later on, I found out that the old people, including my parents-- the educated ones-- they-- they could listen to BBC broadcasts.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And what this is just-- I didn't know it at that time, but I found out since then that the BBC was broadcasting from end of '43.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They knew it that there are gas chambers in-- in-- somewhere in-- they didn't know the name Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But in Poland, Jews are being gassed in great numbers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And these old people-- they listened to it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They knew it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They listened to the English language broadcasts, sometimes even Hungarian language broadcasts.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they all knew it, that they are going to die.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
